keyFacts: The document records a financial transaction involving Jeffrey Epstein.
The transaction was an incoming transfer of assets valued at over $53 million.
The transfer was rejected, indicating potential issues with the transaction.
The document includes references to Southern Financial LLC and Pershing Division of Donaldson.
The transaction was created and last reported on February 7 and 8, 2019, respectively.
